[{"title":"快速開始使用Hexo","url":"/2024/09/20/%E5%BF%AB%E9%80%9F%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8Hexo/","content":"<h4 id=\"下載安裝\"><a href=\"#下載安裝\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"下載安裝\"></a>下載安裝</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Install Hexo</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h4 id=\"建立網站\"><a href=\"#建立網站\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"建立網站\"></a>建立網站</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># create a site</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo init blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"設置主題\"><a href=\"#設置主題\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"設置主題\"></a>設置主題</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 切換至blog目錄</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ <span class=\"built_in\">cd</span> blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 下載主題</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ git <span class=\"built_in\">clone</span> https://github.com/theme-next/hexo-theme-next.git themes\\next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 編輯配置文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ cursor _config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Extensions</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">theme:</span> <span class=\"string\">next</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"運行網站\"><a href=\"#運行網站\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"運行網站\"></a>運行網站</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># start the server</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 訪問網站</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ http://localhost:4000</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["Hexo"]},{"title":"部署Hexo到GitHub Pages","url":"/2024/09/21/%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2Hexo%E5%88%B0GitHub-Pages/","content":"<h4 id=\"操作步驟\"><a href=\"#操作步驟\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"操作步驟\"></a>操作步驟</h4><ol>\n<li>建立一個與GitHub帳號同名的儲存庫，例如: <code>tpdnxu.github.io</code></li>\n<li>安裝部署到GitHub的相關套件</li>\n<li>修改配置文件的Deployment設定</li>\n<li>執行部署命令<span id=\"more\"></span></li>\n</ol>\n<h4 id=\"操作使用\"><a href=\"#操作使用\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"操作使用\"></a>操作使用</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安裝Git部署套件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 編輯配置文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ cursor _confiy.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight yaml\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># URL</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">url:</span> <span class=\"string\">https://tpdnxu.github.io</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">permalink:</span> <span class=\"string\">:year/:month/:day/:title/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">permalink_defaults:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">pretty_urls:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">trailing_index:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span> <span class=\"comment\"># Set to false to remove trailing &#x27;index.html&#x27; from permalinks</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">trailing_html:</span> <span class=\"literal\">true</span> <span class=\"comment\"># Set to false to remove trailing &#x27;.html&#x27; from permalinks</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># Deployment</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"attr\">deploy:</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">type:</span> <span class=\"string\">git</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">repo:</span> <span class=\"string\">git@github.com:tpdnxu/tpdnxu.github.io.git</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attr\">branch:</span> <span class=\"string\">master</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 直接部署檔案到GitHub，不用暫存提交</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">$ hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo deploy --generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","categories":["應用工具"],"tags":["Hexo"]}]